description:
This is a 35 minute workout called '35 MIN GENTLE PILATES || Full Body Workout (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This 35 Minute Gentle Pilates Workout is perfect for those days when you need to slow things down and re-connect with your body and breath. This class is perfect for a morning or evening practice, moving the body gently but still providing an effective workout.
